  "description": "This bright stew has a nice acidity, thanks to green bell peppers and olives, and tender chicken thighs or legs. It takes time to brown the chicken on all sides before adding it to the stew, but it makes the skin nice and tasty. Could be equally great for a family dinner, or for a celebration with friends.",
