  "steps": [
    {
      "name": "",
      "steps": [
        {
          "text": "Rinse and dry chicken thighs. Season with salt and black pepper on both sides and put back in the fridge for several hours.",
          "pause": true
        },
        {
          "text": "Prepare the vegetables. **Onion:** peel, halve, and cut it into 1/2 cm slices. **Garlic:** peel, and cut into 1/2 cm pieces. **Chili:** halve, remove the seeds, and thinly slice.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "In a Dutch oven sat on medium heat, with a generous amount of olive oil, sear the chicken on all sides, until brown and crisp.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "While the chicken is browning, prepare the rest of the vegetables. **Potatoes, beets, and carrots:** peel (if needed), and cut into 2 cm cubes. **Bell peppers:** remove the seeds, and cut into 1x4 cm stripes. **Tomatoes:** remove the roots, and cut into 3 cm cubes.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Remove the chicken from the Dutch oven.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Sauté the onion, garlic, and chili in the Dutch oven until transparent and starting to brown.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add the potatoes, beets, and carrots, and cook for 5 more minutes, stirring occasionally.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add the bell peppers, olives, and more salt, and cook for 5 more minutes, stirring occasionally.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add the tomatoes, and chicken stock. Add ground cumin, cumin seeds, black peppercorns, smoked paprika powder, curcuma powder, and chili flakes. Bring to a boil, lower the heat to low, place the chicken on top of the vegetables, and cook covered for about 40 minutes, until the vegetables are tender.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add more salt if needed, and serve.",
          "pause": false
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
